PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782442073
OL,3,CHeatwaves expose the UK's need to
OL,4,Cfuture-proof its infrastructure
OL,6,FWhile temperatures may be rising in
OL,7,Fthe climate debate, there is no doubt
OL,8,Fthat outside the temperatures are
OL,9,Fsoaring. As the UK faces its hottest
OL,10,Fever May and June, the infrastructure
OL,11,Fand services built for a cooler world
OL,12,Fare under strain.
